CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Springview Holdings through its indirect wholly owned subsidiary, Springview Enterprises, designs and constructs residential and commercial buildings in Singapore. Our projects cover four main types of work: (i) new construction, (ii) reconstruction, (iii) additions and alterations (A&A), and (iv) other general contracting services. Our projects are carried out in either (a) design and build mode or (b) construction mode. When we play a design and build role, we provide design input and also serve as the main contractor.
